# ⚔️ Difference Between wget and curl

| Feature         | wget                     | curl                        |
| --------------- | ------------------------ | --------------------------- |
| Purpose         | Download files           | Transfer data (API, web)    |
| Output          | Saves file automatically | Shows output in terminal    |
| Protocols       | HTTP, HTTPS, FTP         | HTTP, HTTPS, FTP, SCP, etc. |
| Resume download | Yes                      | Limited                     |
| API calls       | Not ideal                | Best suited                 |
| Upload data     | No                       | Yes                         |
| Ease of use     | Simple                   | Flexible                    |

### Examples

```bash
wget https://example.com/file.zip
curl https://example.com
curl -o file.zip https://example.com/file.zip
```

